  (function () {
    var noop = function noop() {};
    if ("performance" in window === false) {
      window.performance = {};
    }
    window.performance.mark = performance.mark || noop;
    window.performance.measure = performance.measure || noop;
    if ("now" in window.performance === false) {
      var nowOffset = Date.now();
      if (performance.timing && performance.timing.navigationStart) {
        nowOffset = performance.timing.navigationStart;
      }
      window.performance.now = function now() {
        return Date.now() - nowOffset;
      };
    }
  })();

<script id="wix-first-paint">
    if (window.ResizeObserver &&
        (!window.PerformanceObserver || !PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes || PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes.indexOf('paint') === -1)) {
        new ResizeObserver(function (entries, observer) {
            entries.some(function (entry) {
                var contentRect = entry.contentRect;
                if (contentRect.width > 0 && contentRect.height > 0) {
                    requestAnimationFrame(function (now) {
                        window.wixFirstPaint = now;
                        dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('wixFirstPaint'));
                    });
                    observer.disconnect();
                    return true;
                }
            });
        }).observe(document.body);
    }
</script>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:30px; line-height:1em; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:30px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_0802e4_4b55253caf1c4f69a9cda07c48962011,wf_4b55253caf1c4f69a9cda07c4,orig_bebas_neue_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-style:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:0em;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:0.1em;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-style:italic;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_18 wixui-rich-text__text" style="color:#0C8444;">truth</span></span></span><span style="font-style:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:0.1em;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_14 wixui-rich-text__text" style="color:#404040;">, </span></span></span><span style="letter-spacing:0.1em;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-style:italic;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_18 wixui-rich-text__text" style="color:#0C8444;">beauty</span></span></span><span style="font-style:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:0.1em;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_14 wixui-rich-text__text" style="color:#404040;"> and </span></span></span><span style="letter-spacing:0.1em;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-style:italic;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_18 wixui-rich-text__text" style="color:#0C8444;">goodness</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p></div><div id="comp-lgq05wxl" class="comp-lgq05wxl KcgtjV wixui-horizontal-line is-animating" data-angle="0" data-angle-style-location="style" data-screen-in-hide="done" style="opacity: 0.9849; transform-origin: 50% 50%; transform: perspective(200px) translate3d(32.1451px, 0px, -0.76077px) rotateY(2.7115deg); visibility: inherit;"><div class="fJrbuY"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="comp-kzri2sav" class="comp-kzri2sav CohWsy wixui-column-strip"><div id="bgLayers_comp-kzri2sav" data-hook="bgLayers" data-motion-part="BG_LAYER" class="if7Vw2"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="tcElKx i1tH8h"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-kzri2sav" data-motion-part="BG_MEDIA" class="wG8dni"></div></div><div data-testid="columns" class="V5AUxf"><div id="comp-kzri2uc5" class="comp-kzri2uc5 YzqVVZ wixui-column-strip__column"><div id="bgLayers_comp-kzri2uc5" data-hook="bgLayers" data-motion-part="BG_LAYER" class="MW5IWV"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="LWbAav Kv1aVt"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-kzri2uc5" data-motion-part="BG_MEDIA" class="VgO9Yg"><wow-image id="img_comp-kzri2uc5" class="HlRz5e Kv1aVt dLPlxY mNGsUM bgImage" data-image-info="{&quot;containerId&quot;:&quot;comp-kzri2uc5&quot;,&quot;alignType&quot;:&quot;center&quot;,&quot;displayMode&quot;:&quot;fill&quot;,&quot;targetWidth&quot;:490,&quot;targetHeight&quot;:804,&quot;isLQIP&quot;:true,&quot;imageData&quot;:{&quot;width&quot;:4000,&quot;height&quot;:2667,&quot;uri&quot;:&quot;54fe5b_eb853c7acd7a400e82688adf802a4183~mv2.jpg&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;displayMode&quot;:&quot;fill&quot;}}" data-bg-effect-name="" data-has-ssr-src="" data-src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/54fe5b_eb853c7acd7a400e82688adf802a4183~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_490,h_804,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_auto/54fe5b_eb853c7acd7a400e82688adf802a4183~mv2.jpg"><img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/54fe5b_eb853c7acd7a400e82688adf802a4183~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_490,h_804,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_auto/54fe5b_eb853c7acd7a400e82688adf802a4183~mv2.jpg" alt="625.jpg" style="width: 490px; line-height:1em; text-align:justify;"><span style="font-size:34px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_0802e4_4b55253caf1c4f69a9cda07c48962011,wf_4b55253caf1c4f69a9cda07c4,orig_bebas_neue_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_15 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-style:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">What is the chief end of education in today’s world? How do we get our children there, wherever “there” may be?</span></span></span></span></span></span></p></div><div id="comp-kzri7gln" class="c9GqVL QxJLC3 comp-kzri7gln wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px; line-height:1.5em; text-align:justify;"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#000000;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:18px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-style:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Is it enough to prepare our children adequately for primary school? Is the goal of setting our children up for a lifetime of academic and employment success doing them justice?</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px; line-height:1.5em; text-align:justify;"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#000000;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:18px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-style:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text">​</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px; line-height:1.5em; text-align:justify;"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#000000;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:18px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-style:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">At Presbyterian Preschool Services, we believe that the above goals, as pragmatic as they are, is far too short-sighted for our children’s own good. </span></span></span></span></span><span class="color_18 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_3a4612c531d149e89813dc52a679f440,wf_3a4612c531d149e89813dc52a,orig_glacialindifferencebold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:18px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-style:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">We aim to break the traditional, meritocratic education goals with the Truth, Beauty and Goodness curriculum framework.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px; line-height:1.5em; text-align:justify;"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#000000;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:18px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-style:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text">​</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:18px; line-height:1.5em; text-align:justify;"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#000000;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_daf7bc_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c213f6cc9,wf_2c225a00c0e343388d96171c2,orig_glacial_indifference_regular;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:18px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-style:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">In short, the TBG Curriculum Framework is our response to a world where truth is often distorted, beauty corrupted and goodness disregarded.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p></div><div id="comp-lca7max9" class="comp-lca7max9" data-semantic-classname="button"><a data-testid="linkElement" href="https://www.presbypreschool.edu.sg/post/the-truth-beauty-and-goodness-curriculum" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="StylableButton2545352419__root style-lh3swl3n__root wixui-button StylableButton2545352419__link" aria-label="READ ABOUT WHY TBG MATTERS"><div class="StylableButton2545352419__container"><span class="StylableButton2545352419__label wixui-button__label" data-testid="stylablebutton-label">READ ABOUT WHY TBG MATTERS</span><span class="StylableButton2545352419__icon wixui-button__icon" aria-hidden="true" data-testid="stylablebutton-icon"><div><svg data-bbox="13.05 2.55 33.878 54.8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 60 60">
